    "name": "Vivat Slovakia",
    "steam_appid": 2132690,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">《Vivat Slovakia》是一款开放世界游戏，设定在新独立的斯洛伐克，这个国家位于东西方的交界处。随着共产主义的遗留影响仍在，衰弱的机构使得腐败猖獗，权力落入出价最高者之手。在金钱与暴力的推动下，“狂野90年代”时代将一个充满阴谋与危险的城市呈现给你。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132690/extras/cc68395fb4c6a3d60b00910abce53d83.avif?t=1763388731\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132690/extras_big/cc68395fb4c6a3d60b00910abce53d83.avif?t=1763388731 width=800 height=122 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132690/extras/586ba9126dd74f17a8f69668dd235af4.poster.avif?t=1763388731\" width=602 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132690/extras/586ba9126dd74f17a8f69668dd235af4.webm?t=1763388731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132690/extras/586ba9126dd74f17a8f69668dd235af4.mp4?t=1763388731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">发现90年代布拉迪斯拉发的粗犷魅力，展现在一个忠实重现的10平方公里范围内，繁忙的街道和历史地标应有尽有。扮演一名卧底国家安全人员，伪装成出租车司机，探索一座反映出介于共产主义与资本主义之间动荡时代的城市，所有的真实商业、住宅和聚会场所都经过精心转化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的动态开放世界设计邀请你深入一个丰富细致的环境，亲眼见证斯洛伐克首都在其未经驯化的斯拉夫荣耀下的模样。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132690/extras/179bd288ee0071813482d23e19ddd9d1.avif?t=1763388731\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132690/extras_big/179bd288ee0071813482d23e19ddd9d1.avif?t=1763388731 width=800 height=122 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132690/extras/640f8f85ee25238de23f84a3dfdc59e2.poster.avif?t=1763388731\" width=602 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132690/extras/640f8f85ee25238de23f84a3dfdc59e2.webm?t=1763388731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132690/extras/640f8f85ee25238de23f84a3dfdc59e2.mp4?t=1763388731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在超过50辆车辆的阵容中穿行，每辆车都反映了90年代初斯洛伐克的独特特点。从坚固的社会主义时代工作车到只有精英才负担得起的豪华进口车。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是驾驶捷克老款轿车、经典的德国进口车，还是那个时代的稀有珍品，你都会遇到那些捕捉经济差异和时代风格趋势的车辆。凭借真实的驾驶物理学和对细节的关注，《Vivat Slovakia》中的汽车让玩家通过街道的景象和声音与斯洛伐克历史的重要部分建立联系。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132690/extras/89c911b235c2340390def0a25c783549.avif?t=1763388731\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132690/extras_big/89c911b235c2340390def0a25c783549.avif?t=1763388731 width=800 height=122 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132690/extras/b54687425f419f24872694f6db2b69c4.poster.avif?t=1763388731\" width=602 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132690/extras/b54687425f419f24872694f6db2b69c4.webm?t=1763388731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132690/extras/b54687425f419f24872694f6db2b69c4.mp4?t=1763388731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">踏入一个由真实事件启发的故事，编织出忠诚、腐败和对权力的渴望。玩家将揭开复杂的关系和不断变化的联盟，努力在一个政治议程与犯罪企业常常交织的世界中生存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个任务都旨在反映90年代的历史冲突，从国家安全的阴影操作，到塑造国家命运的地下交易。游戏通过专业配音演员的才能将这个扣人心弦的故事栩栩如生地呈现出来，增强沉浸感，强化生存与正义的斗争。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132690/extras/0a12c779156ae9e86d531ba09cbe2827.avif?t=1763388731\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132690/extras_big/0a12c779156ae9e86d531ba09cbe2827.avif?t=1763388731 width=800 height=122 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132690/extras/bd7c60f1cc525ace354829aee455943c.poster.avif?t=1763388731\" width=602 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132690/extras/bd7c60f1cc525ace354829aee455943c.webm?t=1763388731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132690/extras/bd7c60f1cc525ace354829aee455943c.mp4?t=1763388731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >90年代的布拉迪斯拉发是一个充满权力斗争的战场，帮派主宰着这座城市，与政府有强大政治关系。执法薄弱，组织犯罪常在白天肆意运作，甚至获得政府的保护。日常生活中包括爆炸、敲诈等现象，敌对帮派在争夺地盘时展开生死搏斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Vivat Slovakia》让玩家能够身临其境地体验这一切，游戏中包含了多种90年代真实的武器，这些武器常见于执法人员和犯罪分子手中。这个时代最臭名昭著的武器，捕捉了在一个“你没有的东西，就必须偷来”的系统中生存的精髓。</p>",
